My dog JC has been going to Villa la Paws since 2010 and she loves it! Daycare, slumber parties and grooming - they do it all!   JC frequently gets groomed at Villa la Paws - they are absolutely the best! I won't take JC anywhere else.  JC has celebrated her last 3 birthdays at Villa la Paws. The staff are just so incredible! They are patient, fun, loving, kind and yet firm when they need to be. They make such a big deal when JC comes in that I just always leave feeling so confident that she is in the best hands!   Best part? Especially if you're worried about leaving your fur kid for several days? They have live cams! Yep, all you have to do is go on the website or, wait for it, there's an app for it! I frequently check on JC using my iPhone or iPad app - it's so awesome!  Thank you Villa la Paws!

