I found The Art of Touch through my friend Lisa who happens to work there - well what a find! The space is in downtown Phoenix and incredibly charming with a very zen and cool funky vibe! Christine, Lisa and Tracy are absolutely the best professional masseuses in the Valley! I've been lucky to have several massages from each and they are so attentive and thorough - an incredible treat every single time! I cannot say enough good things about this place! Highly recommend! Take advantage of the Yelp and Living Social deals!

